text: Cuba national volleyball team is the national volleyball team of Cuba. == Honors == * Olympics: Bronze medal (1976) * World Championship: Silver Medal (1990, 2010) * NORCECA Championship: Gold medal (969, 1971, 1975, 1977, 1979, 1981, 1987, 1989, 1991, 1993, 1995, 1997, 2001, 2009, 2011) - Silver medal (1973, 1985, 1999, 2005) * World League: Gold medal (1998) - Silver medal (1991, 1992, 1994, 1997, 1999) == References == * www.cubanav.org - Cuba Volleyball Federation Category:National volleyball teams Category:Sport in Cuba Category:Organizations based in Cuba Category:National sports teams of Cuba
